		<hr size="1">well, like above poster said, sirens is a 3 tick song. Bravura used to be, but now lasts a minute. also, you used to be able to refresh your charm by pulsing it. ie-</P><P>3 adds. charm, mez, mez, charm, mez, mez, charm, mez, mez would keep all three locked down. With Bravura, you cant refresh it, and since the 2002(?) charm change, maybe you cant pulse the 29 charm anymore. I'm not sure.</P><P>In a dungeon like seb or such, if we get a really bad pull, like 4-5 for reason, I *will* use bravura. thats one mob out of the fight for 1 minute who is also assisting you, and the other 3 I chain mez while they kill the fifth.</P><P>I have a hotkey on page two (bard is the only character where I have 4 pages of hotkeys I constantly use, hehe) that reads "%T is charmed". I just mash that when I charm something, so the group knows not to offtank it. I also use a mez hotkey in pickup groups, since theyre the ones who suck at assist.</P><P><A HREF="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1653" TARGET="_BLANK">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1653</A></P><P>and</P><P><A HREF="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7748" TARGET="_BLANK">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7748</A></P><P>are your big clickies. Goblin ghazi will break any charm, since IVU will break any charm, not just animals.</P><P>Tiny cloak is doable at level 55+ or so, I reccomend a great guide over at concert hall. </P><P><A HREF="http://pub147.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessage?topicID=17785.topic" TARGET="_BLANK">http://pub147.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessage?topicID=17785.topic</A></P><P>FM may be a neccesity. Best AA ever <img src='http://www.everlore.com/gimages/smile.gif' width=15 height=15 align=middle></P><P>hope that helps, I'm not too great at explaining stuff.</P><P></P><P></P><P><BR>Message edited by: Tolain Durant (9/10/2003 1:19:59 PM)<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
