		<hr size="1">Oh, a tip about the meleeing. you neednt stop meleeing except for a breif second. bards can switch targets after a spell starts. example</P><P>Melee mob one<BR>switch targets to mob two and start mez song<BR>quickly switch targets back to mob your meleeing and continue to attack</P><P><BR>I didnt learn that one until well into the 40-50s, but you really only need to target each mob for a second, and then switch back while the song is still preparring to cast<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
